			<div class="content" id="post-content-4540506">
									

<p>I think what did it for me was the pun title. Like, that was enough to get the idea across. Using it <em>again</em> the way you did sunk the connection before I even got to the crosslink. It's a very subtle and genius move, which is a weird thing to say, given&#8230; you know.</p>
<p>MC&amp;D outsourcing to dado is also just a fun image. I'd say that this was a known mistake, given that it isn't the first time they've heard of dado (he gets a mention in <a href="/hypnotraline">Hypnotraline</a>), but I'm willing to forfeit that this is a different universe for obvious reasons.</p>
<p>Upvoted.</p>

